snippet.title:
#amberheard #sketch
Drawing Amber heard
snippet.description:
In this video i am drawing #amberheard #sketch .Amber Laura Heard is an American actress. She made her film debut in 2004 in the sports drama Friday Night Lights. After small roles in North Country and Alpha Dog, Heard played her first leading role in All the Boys Love Mandy Lane and appeared in The CW television show Hidden Palms .
It took me 2 hrs to draw this sketch.
I hope u all like it.
Don't forget to subscribe my channel. 
Thanks for watching.
